  m_Name: Trial of Calling 2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestDefinition
  QuestId: Trial of Calling 2
  QuestTitle: Trial of Calling 2
  QuestObjective: Summon 15 Minions
  QuestDescription: You are asked, without judgment or urgency, to gather fifteen
    more creatures to stand beside you in service of 'performing massage and work'.
    Seek those whose youth has not yet faded, for they are said to be more responsive
    to instruction. The reason is not shared, and none is expected. Simply bring
    them when you can.
  QuestOutcome: "As each creature manifests, you feel it again\u2014that subtle tightening
    in the atmosphere. Approval? Curiosity?\n\nWhatever watches you seems less interested
    in your companions... and more interested in whether they come willingly."
  MaxProgress: 15
